{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/887090/extras/Title1_RichardIII.png?t=1667052954\" /><br><br><strong>Richard the Third </strong>is an epic two-player wargame that recreates the bloody dynastic struggle in the 15th century between the royal houses of Lancaster and York for the throne of England.<br><br>Will the mad-king Henry VI and his Queen Margaret keep the throne or will the Duke of York recover it for the Plantagenets. Also strutting across the game's stage are Edward IV, Richard III, Henry VII, and Warwick, the notorious &quot;<i>Kingmaker</i>&quot;.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/887090/extras/Title2_Claim_the_Throne.png?t=1667052954\" /><br>The object of play is to eliminate all five enemy heirs and/or win control of the powerful nobles of England. <br>The Lancastrians start the game holding the throne, and the Yorkists are in exile ready to invade. Kingship can be won or lost several times during the game. <br><br>Will Richard III emerge triumphant, or will he perish in battle as he did historically?<br><br>The game is currently 1-player-vs-AI and local-2-player (a.k.a. hot seat)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/887090/extras/SteamStore_Description_Bottom_RichardIII.png?t=1667052954\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887090/f0ea5598af6ea4660614bc3a68b747556647121b.jpg"},{"name":"Headsman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887090/12d16341141cb02c24d127702115c1a98e43fd6b.jpg"},{"name":"Nemesis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887090/9d2d02463bcf0ae6911c63dcf7328efa45457b72.jpg"},{"name":"Commander","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/publ